description: Try our easy to follow Easy Pork Sausage Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Sausage rolls,Sausage,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,High protein,Mince,Pork,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Easy Pork Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Line 2 baking trays with baking paper. Mix pork mince, vegetables, garlic and egg together and season with salt and pepper.
Cut each pastry sheet in half. Form 1/2 cup amounts into a long sausage shape and place onto one edge of each sheet of pastry. Roll up to enclose.
Glaze outside of pastry with egg wash. Cut into small bite-sized pieces (5-6 per roll) and place onto trays.
Cook for 15-20 minutes until golden brown.
